      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like my brain is just... fundamentally bugged. like the hardware is faulty and no amount of software updates or therapy is gonna fix the core architecture. it feels like i was just born with a massive error in the code. is there even any point in trying to fix something that was born broken?",
